home.title: Welcome Home
home.data:
iKnow Church Software is a feature packed church management solution. It provides all the great database functionality you would expect whilst adding some unbelievable benefits too. One of the many benefits is being able to have your own mobile app for yur church! Your own branded and designed APP in the store under your church name just like this one. What is great about it is not only is it free (apart form a small design fee) its content is upto date and fresh all driven form the iKnow System.

Check out www.iknowchurchsoftware.com

Here are just some of the features:

About Example

Church News

Videos Whats on Calendar

Podcasts - Videos

Prayer Requests

Teams info & Serving Reminders

Ticket Purchase for Events

Map Meet Up - see friends on map and connect

Social Feeds - Twitter, Facebook, Instagram, vimeo etc...
